-post_type_archive nav__menu-item--object-book nav__menu-item--179 nav__menu-item--level-0"><a class="nav__link" href="https://www.journalofdemocracy.org/books/">Books</a></li><li class=" nav__menu-item nav__menu-item--type-post_type nav__menu-item--object-page nav__menu-item--current-page-parent nav__menu-item--184 nav__menu-item--has-children nav__menu-item--level-0"><a class="nav__link" href="https://www.journalofdemocracy.org/news/">News &#038; Features</a><button class="nav__menu-toggle">+</button><ul class="nav__menu nav__menu--level-1"><li class=" nav__menu-item nav__menu-item--type-custom nav__menu-item--object-custom nav__menu-item--4830 nav__menu-item--level-1"><a class="nav__link" href="https://www.journalofdemocracy.org/news/">Main</a></li><li class=" nav__menu-item nav__menu-item--type-custom nav__menu-item--object-custom nav__menu-item--3719 nav__menu-item--level-1"><a class="nav__link" href="https://www.journalofdemocracy.org/articles/supplements/">Article Supplements</a></li><li class=" nav__menu-item nav__menu-item--type-custom nav__menu-item--object-custom nav__menu-item--4833 nav__menu-item--level-1"><a class="nav__link" href="https://www.journalofdemocracy.org/jod-content-now-available-in-apple-books-format/">EBook Downloads</a></li><li class=" nav__menu-item nav__menu-item--type-custom nav__menu-item--object-custom nav__menu-item--4834 nav__menu-item--level-1"><a class="nav__link" href="https://www.journalofdemocracy.org/podcasts/">Podcasts</a></li></ul></li><li class=" nav__menu-item nav__menu-item--type-custom nav__menu-item--object-custom nav__menu-item--5707 nav__menu-item--level-0"><a class="nav__link" href="https://www.journalofdemocracy.org/subscribe/">Subscribe</a></li></ul></nav>
