		<div class="article__header-wrap">
			<h1 class="article__title">The Miracle and Tragedy of the 2020 U.S. Election</h1>

				<ul class="authors article__authors">
				<li class="authors__author"><a href="https://www.journalofdemocracy.org/authors/nathaniel-persily/">Nathaniel Persily</a></li>
				<li class="authors__author"><a href="https://www.journalofdemocracy.org/authors/charles-stewart-iii/">Charles Stewart III</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>

